//Mass/Tumor - Characterization I - I know


Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Yes' radio button in 'CM reinforced' box in Page 03
And	I'm on Page 08 of Cardiac MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Mass/Tumor' from the dropdown menu
And I select 'I know' radio button box

Then multiple selection Localizer is enabled
And 'Diameter max. axially' input field is enabled

And 'Differential diagnosis 1' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Signal behavior T1w' slide bar is enabled
And 'Signal behavior T2w' slide bar is enabled

And 'Well defined' radio button is enabled
And 'Ill defined' radio button is enabled
And 'Irregular' radio button is enabled

And 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled

And 'Yes' radio button is enabled
And 'No' radio button is enabled

When I select all parts on the Localizer
Then all parts are selected and turn red

When I select 'Yes' radio button
Then 'Strong' radio button is enabled
And 'Low' radio button is enabled
And 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled
